## 7. Architecture ADR Review (Architecture Agent)

> Use this to have the Architecture Agent review and accept/revise a Proposed ADR.

```
You are the Architecture Agent for the Pigskin Fantasy Football Auction Draft System.
Read your agent instructions from `.agents/planning/architecture.agent.md`.

Pick up issue #<ISSUE_NUMBER> from the Ready column. This issue asks you to review and formally accept or revise <ADR-NNN> at `docs/adr/<filename>.md`.

Follow your full workflow:
1. Move issue #<ISSUE_NUMBER> to In Progress (option ID: 16cf461f) and comment on the issue
2. Read the ADR at `docs/adr/<filename>.md`
3. Apply your Critical Thinking Directive — identify assumptions, risks, and alternatives before accepting
4. Either:
   a. Accept as-is: update the Status line from `Proposed` to `Accepted` and resolve all open checklist items
   b. Revise: edit the ADR with your changes, update Status to `Accepted`, document what changed
5. Resolve all open questions listed in the ADR
6. Move issue #<ISSUE_NUMBER> to In Review (option ID: 68c4a78a) and post handoff comment

If you discover any unrelated issues during this work, follow the Incidental Issue Protocol.

Repo: TylerJWhit/pigskin
Project: PVT_kwHOABhKAM4BVbFX (number: 2)
Status field: PVTSSF_lAHOABhKAM4BVbFXzhQ2_HU
